General Manager - Dubai - Premium Luxury Fashion business
This internationally renowned fashion retail business are currently seeking a General Manager to join them in their flagship location.
The successful candidate will be the key to supporting the on-going success of this high profile brand. They are seeking a retail professional who has had a proven track record of delivering excellent standards, driving service levels and developing strong external results via their teams within high turnover / multi-site environments.
The role of the General Manager is to strategically support the day to day operations of the site including retail operations, Finance and Marketing as well as building strong relationships internally and driving the brand forwards to success.
Excellent package and remuneration for the successful candidate. This job was originally posted as
